    "text": [
        "Dear Mr. Jackie,",
        "I am writing this letter to you  attending your concert in London last week. I am your biggest fan and it was a dream come true moment for me.",
        "The reason I am expressing my feeling here is your performance on the stage was a heart-touching experience.\u00a0Which made the crowd, including me dance relentlessly. I felt your energy how you sang and create an entertaining\u00a0atmosphere for everyone.\u00a0However, the show finished\u00a0soon, but it was a pleasure to see you live.",
        "I would like to share with you my musical interest that is playing guitar. Even though I have been playing for 3 years but could not reach your level. In spite of a lot of practice, I am still lacking in a few areas.",
        "Kindly help me to improve\u00a0my musical skills so that I can perform better. If you can provide me some personal classes in your studio, I will grateful to you.",
        "I hope you do the needful.",
        "Yours Sincerely."
